        <div class="flex-item third"><p>Haribo Gummi Bears</p><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/519JJTm5%2BxL.jpg" alt="haribo" class="fleximg" /></div>
        <div class="flex-item fourth"><p>Nice! Gummy Bears</p><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Voof3WHSvio/UdrizswvTNI/AAAAAAAAAAw/LR_fcjwZXfw/s1600/2.jpg" alt="Nice!" class="fleximg" /></div>

        <div class="flex-item fifth"><p>Jelly Belly Gummy Bears - 12 Count Case</p><img src="https://cdn-tp1.mozu.com/9046-11441/cms/11441/files/0634218a-155f-4e5c-988e-ca30900d16ea" alt="jelly belly" class="fleximg" /></div>
        <div class="flex-item sixth"><p>Albanese Gummy Bears</p><img src="http://bpc.h-cdn.co/assets/16/03/480x480/gallery-1453241053-albanese-gummy-bears.jpg" alt="Albanese" class="fleximg" /></div>
    </div>
